{% comment %}
  ============================================================
  BFC Refurbishment Process Section  (v1)
  ------------------------------------------------------------
  Drop-in section for any 35mm / 120 camera PDP — explains
  why buying from BFC is different from eBay, what we do
  beyond other camera shops, type-specific refurb steps, and
  the risk-removal guarantee.

  Schema "camera_type" dropdown swaps the type-specific copy
  (hero headline + intro + 5 process steps). The pillars and
  the vs-table stay the same across all types.

  Defaults are wired for every type so adding the section to
  a PDP requires zero configuration. Every text field is
  overridable in the customizer if a specific camera needs
  different wording.

  Designed to mirror the collapsible pattern used in the SX-70
  Family Guide section so it feels native to the BFC theme.
  ============================================================
{% endcomment %}

{%- assign t = section.settings.camera_type -%}

{%- comment -%} Resolve the type-specific copy based on the dropdown.
    Each `tX_*` setting overrides the default for that type. {%- endcomment -%}
{%- if t == 'rangefinder' -%}
  {%- assign bar_title_default     = 'How we refurbish every rangefinder' -%}
  {%- assign hero_h_default        = 'A working rangefinder, <em>aligned.</em>' -%}
  {%- assign hero_p_default        = 'A rangefinder is only as good as its patch alignment. Every rangefinder we sell has been opened, cleaned, and re-calibrated so the patch is sharp, the lines up, and the meter reads true.' -%}
  {%- assign proc_h_default        = 'The rangefinder refurb process' -%}
  {%- assign proc_intro_default    = 'Rangefinders need different care than SLRs. Here is the short version.' -%}
  {%- assign step1_h_default       = 'Open and inspect' -%}
  {%- assign step1_p_default       = 'Log shutter, patch, and meter issues.' -%}
  {%- assign step2_h_default       = 'Service the shutter' -%}
  {%- assign step2_p_default       = 'Cleaned and re-lubed at every speed.' -%}
  {%- assign step3_h_default       = 'Realign the RF patch' -%}
  {%- assign step3_p_default       = 'Vertical, horizontal, and infinity dialed in.' -%}
  {%- assign step4_h_default       = 'Clean the optics' -%}
  {%- assign step4_p_default       = 'Viewfinder, RF window, and beamsplitter.' -%}
  {%- assign step5_h_default       = 'QC and warranty' -%}
  {%- assign step5_p_default       = 'Final check, second tech, on the shelf.' -%}
{%- elsif t == 'mf-slr' -%}
